    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 full transparency is important to us. The car shows significant wear throughout, including visible body damage, rust in multiple areas, and an interior that is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional components. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require substantial work before it can be considered reliable daily transportation. It starts and moves under its own power, but expect to invest considerable time and money into repairs. This listing is best suited for a dedicated DIY mechanic, a restoration hobbyist, or someone seeking it for parts. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get. Sold as-is with no warranty implied.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car. The exterior shows only minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 you may notice a few small scratches or light scuffs here and there, but there are no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains a healthy shine with no major fading. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; upholstery shows modest signs of use but nothing torn or heavily worn. All major features and controls operate as intended, including climate control, infotainment, windows, and mirrors. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, transmission shifts smoothly, and brakes feel responsive. It has been serviced regularly, and there are no warning lights on the dashboard. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid everyday driver that won't surprise you with hidden issues \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that sets the standard for pre-owned excellence. This stunning automobile has been meticulously maintained and presents in flawless, showroom-ready condition \u2014 every surface, system, and detail reflecting the care of a discerning owner. The exterior gleams with zero blemishes, the interior is immaculate with no wear whatsoever, and all mechanical systems perform with the precision and confidence of a brand-new vehicle. Documented service history, clean title, and a full inspection on file. Opportunities like this are rare \u2014 don't let it pass you by.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
